true_SQL: SELECT T3.born_state FROM department AS T1 JOIN management AS T2 ON T1.department_id  =  T2.department_id JOIN head AS T3 ON T2.head_id  =  T3.head_id WHERE T1.name  =  'Treasury' INTERSECT SELECT T3.born_state FROM department AS T1 JOIN management AS T2 ON T1.department_id  =  T2.department_id JOIN head AS T3 ON T2.head_id  =  T3.head_id WHERE T1.name  =  'Homeland Security'
qSQL: SELECT DISTINCT h1.born_state FROM head h1 JOIN management m1 ON h1.head_ID = m1.head_ID JOIN department d1 ON m1.Department_ID = d1.Department_ID JOIN head h2 ON m2.head_ID = m2.head_ID JOIN management m2 ON h2.head_ID = m2.head_ID JOIN department d2 ON m2.Department_ID = d2.Department_ID WHERE d1.Name = 'Treasury' AND d2.Name = 'Homeland Security' AND h1.born_state = h2.born_state;
